---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---

<footer class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-white py-12">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
          Workmate AI <span class="text-brand-600">·</span>
          <span class="text-brand-600">Đồng nghiệp AI của bạn</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm text-gray-600">
          Sản phẩm của AI Workforce Solutions. Desktop AI assistant & agent automation platform cho người Việt.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Sản phẩm</h4>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li><a href="#download" class="hover:text-brand-600">Tải bản OpenCode</a></li>
          <li><a href="#download" class="hover:text-brand-600">Tải bản OpenClaw</a></li>
          <li><a href="#features" class="hover:text-brand-600">Tính năng</a></li>
          <li><a href="#faq" class="hover:text-brand-600">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Liên hệ</h4>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li><a href="mailto:info@aiws.vn" class="hover:text-brand-600">info@aiws.vn</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://aiws.vn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-brand-600">aiws.vn</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/AI-Workforce-Solutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-brand-600">GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
        © {year} AI Workforce Solutions. Workmate AI là sản phẩm độc lập. Bản OpenCode xây dựng trên <a href="https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline">OpenCode</a> (MIT) — không liên kết với Anomaly Innovations, Inc.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
